rom\": 820, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"an unprecedented 200 meters\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal ceremony\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both swims were completed in Olympic record time, a remarkable feat in two of the most tiring and demanding disciplines.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both swims\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic record time\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"the most tiring and demanding disciplines\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until Wednesday, no swimmer had managed to medal in both.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"no swimmer\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was pretty crazy to have the chance to be in the final in both races,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"both races\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then I just loved it, it was huge.\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have fulfilled a lot of dreams since I have been here.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1287}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing this double was also something I felt capable of, but to really do it in the real world is something else.\\\"\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the real world\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With passion, patriotic pride and raw emotion bursting out on all sides, Marchand soaked up the pressure and delivered what even the hype had suggested might be too much.\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"passion\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"patriotic pride\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"raw emotion\", \"from\": 1471, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"all sides\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1508}, {\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1541}, {\"ngram\": \"even the hype\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The winner of Sunday's Individual Medley started with an incredible comeback in the butterfly after Hungarian world record holder and reigning champion Kristof Milak led the first three lengths.\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999999997307896, \"rank\": 2.149491610951756e-10, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"score\": 0.9886078568488, \"rank\": 0.01152338471634019, \"text\": \"Milak\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Milak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The winner\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1619}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday's Individual Medley\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1649}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible comeback\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"the butterfly\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the first three lengths\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Milak had to settle for silver, with Canada's Ilya Kharun taking bronze.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 1877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 18